data.title: “When I was with her, I knew I was home": Mary Anne O'Neal
data.meta_description: Dr. Mary Anne O’Neal of Athens, Georgia died on June 17, 2023 after living with appendix cancer for over 10 years. Born in Bennettsville, South Carolina on May 17, 1963, she was a graduate of Marlboro Academy (SC), earned her B.A. in English at Mars Hill College in 1985, her M.A. Ed. from Western Carolina University in 1988, and her Ph.D.
